the war bride is a 2001 canadian/british drama film .   the film was directed by lyndon chubbuck and written by angela workman .   the film stars anna friel as lily and julie cox as sophie , two young women from london , england who marry canadian soldiers ( aden young and benjamin boyd ) during world war ii , and move to canada as war brides .   the film 's cast also includes brenda fricker , caroline cave and molly parker .